        [
          "Your a secure courier, moving packages and passenger and the occasional document that is too sensitive for transmission.  You were embraced barely before the Schism and the Camarilla seemed much more appealing than a bunch of Genocidal Technophobes with many guns.  Of course, no few princes are leery of telecommunications themselves so now your carrying a lot of personal commuications between cities like a glorified pony express withi fangs.",
